headline: Gartner, HP, Globalstar, Amphenol, and Equifax Stocks Trade Up, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after the latest Consumer Price Index (CPI) report came in softer than anticipated, fueling investor optimism for interest rate cuts by the Federal Reserve.

headline: PayPal Stock Falls 31% as New CEO Inherits Execution Crisis
summary: If you have been closely watching shares of PayPal (NASDAQ:PYPL), you haven’t missed its 30.7% collapse year-to-date, with retail investor sentiment on Reddit turning sharply bearish. The fintech pioneer’s weekly sentiment score plunged to 37, down from a neutral 57.4 over the past month, as traders digested a brutal earnings miss and disappointing 2026 guidance. ...
